{"tid":1872694,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"今日番工屌撚到個00後喊","createTime":"2020-02-10T08:10:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T16:17:19.000Z","uid":158407,"like":28,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"9621aea06be577a3a395dd8c330bd82d023e1d2d","tid":1872694,"uid":158407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T08:10:25.000Z","msg":"開會個時老細要搵3條友上大陸盤點，我即刻點名叫左個00後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢驚驚地咁話，「下呢家上面咁樣唔係咁好wor」屌你老味聽到火都泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一野拍台同佢講個會唔洗開啦同我出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢喊晒口話比次機會佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />見佢眼濕濕老細都叫佢留番係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n完左個會老細叫左佢入佢房，我扮走入去攞野比老細加鹽加醋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />條00後話咩無回鄉證，我即刻開佢IG show比老細睇佢同班friend之前上去飲喜茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />條00後即刻狡辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />話咩過咗期，最後迫埋佢攞張回鄉證出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />老細嬲到震話要佢一定要上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪再講大話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係就要炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢喊晒口咁走左去廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑撚到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87116fc4a1266ad82da9bb33c8f8b7f1dc40f98d","tid":1872694,"uid":219583,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T08:13:27.000Z","msg":"已閱"},{"pid":"410b3e77819c9fa8d4b0b5f03cf433dafdd702f4","tid":1872694,"uid":203909,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":